        <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-4025585e-5df0-63e3-021e-450eee80995a"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Welcome to FunFooding.com! The perfect food trading platform (online and mobile) designed to connect diners with home cooks and student chefs listing their delectable home-cooked meals. FunFooding.com springs from the idea of delivering varied dining options from diverse local cuisine to diners in their community.</span></span></p>

        <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-4025585e-5df0-63e3-021e-450eee80995a"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">There are lots of people with no time to cook a healthy, enjoyable meal; others simply aren&rsquo;t in the mood to cook and that&rsquo;s where you come in. As a Food trader, you can showcase your home cooked meals here at FunFooding.com. You present your food items, along with availability and pricing. Diners place an order to pick up the meal you&rsquo;re listing
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
