        <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-4025585e-5df0-63e3-021e-450eee80995a"><span style="font-size: 18.6667px; font-family: Tahoma; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">How to Begin</span></span></p>

        <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-4025585e-5df0-63e3-021e-450eee80995a"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">First,</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> </span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Sign Up for FREE at FunFooding.com. Email and password selection is all that you need to begin!</span></span></p>

        <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-4025585e-5df0-63e3-021e-450eee80995a"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Second,</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> Add the Food Items You are Offering. Keep in mind that you&rsquo;ll need to indicate potential allergy triggers on each of your meal items. Include a photo, so the food circle can feast first with their eyes.</span></span></p>

        <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-4025585e-5df0-63e3-021e-450eee80995a"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Your food list should include unit measure, quantity available and pricing. By the cup would be appropriate for foods like soups, rice, grains, vegetables, etc., ounces would be the unit measure for meats, poultry, seafood, etc., and for pizzas, pies, casseroles, cakes, the measure should be listed as 16 inch pepperoni pizza, 9 inch apple pie, 9 inch 3 layer red velvet cake, 8 x 13 casserole. You&rsquo;ll also want to list how much you have available for purchase, if you have 50 ounces of poultry, you can list five 10 ounce servings or if you have multiple pizzas for sale list the number of whole pizzas. </span></span></p>

        <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-4025585e-5df0-63e3-021e-450eee80995a"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">In setting your price, you&rsquo;ll want to consider the total cost of the food used as well as the time and effort that went into it its preparation. Obviously a pizza wouldn&rsquo;t be as costly as Ch&acirc;teaubriand. You&rsquo;ll also need to consider the cost of the dish at popular restaurants in your area, so as not to price too low or too high &ndash; but at a fair price that makes your food sharing adventure worthwhile.</span></span></p>

        <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-4025585e-5df0-63e3-021e-450eee80995a"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Once your food item is uploaded, FunFooding.com will quickly approve your entry and you&rsquo;ll be all set to list! Once approved, this meal can be listd multiple times without additional approval.</span></span></p>

        <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-4025585e-5df0-63e3-021e-450eee80995a"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Third,</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> Verify Your Address. At this point, your address is crucial, because people searching in your area don&rsquo;t want to drive an hour in search of your food. They want your fabulous food fast!</span></span></p>

        <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-4025585e-5df0-63e3-021e-450eee80995a"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Fourth,</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> Confirm Your Account Settings.</span></span></p>

        <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-4025585e-5df0-63e3-021e-450eee80995a"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">FunFooding.com offers three levels of privacy settings similar to </span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Facebook</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">&reg;</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> or Linkedin</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">&reg;. You simply choose the privacy setting that is right for you from the following:</span></span></p>

        <ul style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">
            <li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline;">
                <p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.295; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-4025585e-5df0-63e3-021e-450eee80995a"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">INNER CIRCLE &ndash; This circle forms with people u know, friends and neighbors you&rsquo;ve have invited to join or connected with in the FunFooding community. This is the safest privacy setting, but it is also the most restrictive. </span></span></p>
            </li>
            <li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline;">
